trans-unit.source: Exception occurs if Azure blob name is specified incorrectly.
trans-unit.target: Exception occurs if Azure blob name is specified incorrectly.

trans-unit.source: This exception occurs if the Azure blob name is specified incorrectly.
trans-unit.target: This exception occurs if the Azure blob name is specified incorrectly.

trans-unit.source: You will receive the error if:
trans-unit.target: You will receive the error if:

trans-unit.source: The blob cannot be found in the specified container.
trans-unit.target: The blob cannot be found in the specified container.

trans-unit.source: The fully qualified name of the blob specified for output in one of the <link xlink:href="81c457af-f5c0-4b2d-922c-fdef2274413c" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Learning with counts</link> modules is greater than 512 characters.
trans-unit.target: The fully qualified name of the blob specified for output in one of the <link xlink:href="81c457af-f5c0-4b2d-922c-fdef2274413c" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Learning with counts</link> modules is greater than 512 characters.

trans-unit.source: Only the container was specified as the source in a <link xlink:href="4e1b0fe6-aded-4b3f-a36f-39b8862b9004" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Reader</link> request when the format was Excel or CSV with encoding; concatenation of the contents of all blobs within a container is not allowed with these formats.
trans-unit.target: Only the container was specified as the source in a <link xlink:href="4e1b0fe6-aded-4b3f-a36f-39b8862b9004" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Reader</link> request when the format was Excel or CSV with encoding; concatenation of the contents of all blobs within a container is not allowed with these formats.

trans-unit.source: A SAS URI does not contain the name of a valid blob.
trans-unit.target: A SAS URI does not contain the name of a valid blob.

trans-unit.source: Revisit the module throwing the exception.
trans-unit.target: Revisit the module throwing the exception.

trans-unit.source: Verify that the specified blob does exist in the container in the storage account and that permissions allow you to see the blob.
trans-unit.target: Verify that the specified blob does exist in the container in the storage account and that permissions allow you to see the blob.

trans-unit.source: Verify that the input is of the form <userInputLocalizable>containername/filename</userInputLocalizable> in the case of Excel or CSV with encoding formats.
trans-unit.target: Verify that the input is of the form <userInputLocalizable>containername/filename</userInputLocalizable> in the case of Excel or CSV with encoding formats.

trans-unit.source: Verify that a SAS URI contains the name of a valid blob.
trans-unit.target: Verify that a SAS URI contains the name of a valid blob.

trans-unit.source: The Azure storage blob is incorrect.
trans-unit.target: The Azure storage blob is incorrect.

trans-unit.source: The Azure storage blob name "{0}" is incorrect
trans-unit.target: The Azure storage blob name "{0}" is incorrect
